        <briefdescription>
<para>Scan interval (N * 0.625 ms). </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>When <computeroutput>CONFIG_BT_SCAN_AND_INITIATE_IN_PARALLEL</computeroutput> is enabled and the application wants to scan and connect in parallel, the Bluetooth Controller may require the scan interval used for scanning and connection establishment to be equal to obtain the best performance. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
